sections.heading: Sections; how construed.Sections 70-1701 to 70-1705 shall be liberally construed to effectuate their purposes
sections.text: The provisions of sections 70-1701 to 70-1705 shall be independent of and supplemental to any other applicable provisions of law, petition for creation, or charter.SourceLaws 2004, LB 969,
